job_description: We are looking for a skilled factory worker or engineer to join our team at GE Appliances. The ideal candidate should have experience with manufacturing processes, equipment maintenance, quality control, safety protocols, and working in a fast-paced production environment.
questions: Describe a time you identified and resolved a problem with a piece of manufacturing equipment?
How do you prioritize tasks in a fast-paced production environment with competing deadlines?
Explain your experience with implementing or adhering to safety protocols in a manufacturing setting?
Can you describe your approach to quality control and ensuring product standards are met?
Walk me through a time you had to quickly learn a new manufacturing process or technology?
